has developed too fast.

322
00:19:58,710 --> 00:20:00,860
We'd better be friends.

323
00:20:02,970 --> 00:20:05,280
Gao Zhi Yi, I told you that
you were being self-righteous

324
00:20:05,370 --> 00:20:06,840
and being embarrassed.

325
00:20:06,930 --> 00:20:09,260
You're overthinking.

326
00:20:15,150 --> 00:20:15,390
Yi Yi.

327
00:20:15,480 --> 00:20:17,120
Leave me alone.

328
00:20:17,200 --> 00:20:18,080
Come on.

329
00:20:18,910 --> 00:20:20,420
Yi Yi, don't be sad.

330
00:20:20,500 --> 00:20:22,220
Feng Qi isn't good for you.

331
00:20:28,820 --> 00:20:29,900
Mr Zhang,

332
00:20:30,790 --> 00:20:32,070
What exactly do you

333
00:20:32,160 --> 00:20:34,180
want me to do here today?

334
00:20:34,740 --> 00:20:36,320
Although we are in a
contractual relationship,

335
00:20:36,410 --> 00:20:37,290
