grandpa or our families,

339
00:20:42,260 --> 00:20:43,240
you can present yourself

340
00:20:43,330 --> 00:20:44,770
in a way that's more compatible with me.

341
00:20:51,320 --> 00:20:52,200
A moment please.

342
00:20:57,840 --> 00:20:58,790
Hello,

343
00:20:58,880 --> 00:21:00,670
