348
00:21:15,040 --> 00:21:16,890
Let's go. It's just ahead.

349
00:21:24,820 --> 00:21:25,850
Mr Zhang,

350
00:21:26,550 --> 00:21:28,980
So you brought me here today

351
00:21:29,200 --> 00:21:31,040
