396
00:25:13,430 --> 00:25:14,890
Is there any fresh chicken in the shop?

397
00:25:15,520 --> 00:25:16,390
Yeah.

398
00:25:16,540 --> 00:25:18,230
Do you have linseed oil or olive oil?

399
00:25:18,410 --> 00:25:19,290
Yeah.

400
00:25:19,800 --> 00:25:21,250
You have eggs, flour and bread crumbs

401
00:25:21,330 --> 00:25:22,990
