403
00:25:23,860 --> 00:25:25,460
Then there should be no
difficulty in making a fried chicken.

404
00:25:25,730 --> 00:25:27,430
The oil temperature should
be kept at 180 degrees.

405
00:25:27,600 --> 00:25:29,170
The error should not exceed three degrees.

406
00:25:29,420 --> 00:25:30,950
Only then will it have a nice texture.

407
00:25:31,350 --> 00:25:33,000
I'm sorry, sir. Restaurant policy.

408
00:25:33,090 --> 00:25:34,350
We can only cook what's on the menu.

409
00:25:35,800 --> 00:25:37,000
Mr Zhang,

410
00:25:39,690 --> 00:25:40,650
I remember you.

411
00:25:40,740 --> 00:25:42,220
You’re from Zheng Ben University, right?

412
00:25:42,310 --> 00:25:43,520
In Mr Zhang's class last time,

413
00:25:43,610 --> 00:25:44,920
