414
00:25:45,310 --> 00:25:46,510
Sister, you do have a good memory.

415
00:25:46,600 --> 00:25:47,700
I major in Economics.

416
00:25:47,790 --> 00:25:48,770
This is my senior year.

417
00:25:48,900 --> 00:25:50,680
I often go to Mr Zhang's class secretly.

418
00:25:51,880 --> 00:25:53,050
I'll deal with it.
You go on with other things.

419
00:25:54,330 --> 00:25:54,840
Mr Zhang,

420
00:25:54,930 --> 00:25:56,490
What would you like to eat today?

421
00:25:56,800 --> 00:25:59,050
A seafood salad with vinegar dressing

422
00:25:59,550 --> 00:26:00,730
and a fried chicken

423
00:26:00,880 --> 00:26:01,760
with canola oil.

424
00:26:01,870 --> 00:26:02,780
Fried chicken?

425
00:26:09,150 --> 00:26:10,600
Who told you to add
dishes without permission?

426
00:26:11,550 --> 00:26:13,290
