is all messed up by you.

427
00:26:13,750 --> 00:26:15,490
The dishes they requested
weren't complicated.

428
00:26:15,570 --> 00:26:16,450
So I...

429
00:26:16,810 --> 00:26:18,150
Can you do that as long as
it's not complicated to make?

430
00:26:18,240 --> 00:26:19,060
I just...

431
00:26:19,150 --> 00:26:20,960
Sorry, manager.

432
00:26:21,470 --> 00:26:22,870
Please don't say that about her.

433
00:26:23,060 --> 00:26:24,680
We made her do it.

434
00:26:24,770 --> 00:26:26,580
So please stop blaming her.

435
00:26:29,270 --> 00:26:30,050
Guest.

436
00:26:30,140 --> 00:26:31,630
We have met all your requirements.

437
00:26:31,930 --> 00:26:33,250
Please stop interfering with

438
00:26:33,340 --> 00:26:34,760
my discipline of my employees.

439
00:26:35,120 --> 00:26:36,900
Then you can't personally attack her.

440
00:26:36,990 --> 00:26:38,340
Because she's useless

441
00:26:38,430 --> 00:26:39,660
and ruins business.

442
00:26:41,000 --> 00:26:42,300
On what background can you say that?

443
00:26:42,390 --> 00:26:44,830
If all of your employees were like her,

444
00:26:44,950 --> 00:26:46,330
your restaurant would be better off.

445
00:26:46,420 --> 00:26:47,510
What makes you say that?

446
00:26:47,590 --> 00:26:49,380
Because the other
employees in your restaurant

447
00:26:49,460 --> 00:26:50,640
look unhappy.

448
00:26:50,730 --> 00:26:51,530
She's the only one

449
00:26:51,620 --> 00:26:52,970
who deals with the guests with a smile.

450
00:26:53,850 --> 00:26:55,390
Smile can make more profits?

451
00:26:55,920 --> 00:26:57,350
Why are you all so naive?

452
00:26:57,780 --> 00:26:58,140
You.

453
00:26:58,230 --> 00:26:59,330
This is really not naive.

454
00:27:02,690 --> 00:27:03,940
I'm sure you don't know

455
00:27:04,030 --> 00:27:05,930
the variable relationship between the
index model of customer satisfaction

456
00:27:06,020 --> 00:27:08,350
and beverage profits.

457
00:27:09,250 --> 00:27:11,430
The catering industry
belongs to the service industry.

458
00:27:11,720 --> 00:27:14,210
Customer satisfaction
is the primary productivity.

459
00:27:14,300 --> 00:27:15,950
Instead of blindly rejecting
the guest's request,

460
00:27:16,040 --> 00:27:19,030
it's better to adapt to
meet the needs of guests.

461
00:27:19,340 --> 00:27:21,240
I suggest you study

462
00:27:21,330 --> 00:27:22,500
index models carefully.

463
00:27:22,770 --> 00:27:23,730
If you can't understand,

464
00:27:23,820 --> 00:27:25,150
