465
00:27:25,290 --> 00:27:26,520
And she'll give you all the answers.

466
00:27:26,610 --> 00:27:26,930
Come on.

467
00:27:27,020 --> 00:27:27,850
Besides,

468
00:27:27,940 --> 00:27:28,670
