477
00:27:55,200 --> 00:27:56,780
Then you lied?

478
00:27:56,870 --> 00:27:59,150
A white lie is not a lie.

479
00:27:59,670 --> 00:28:00,880
That's what you said.

480
00:28:21,100 --> 00:28:22,370
Mr Zhang, don't worry

481
00:28:22,450 --> 00:28:24,640
I'll definitely finish reading
these books when I go back.

482
00:28:24,730 --> 00:28:25,610
And

483
00:28:25,830 --> 00:28:27,430
I certainly won't let you down.

484
00:28:28,250 --> 00:28:30,510
I'll do my best in my senior year
to graduate.

485
00:28:31,570 --> 00:28:32,450
What about after that?

486
00:28:36,550 --> 00:28:37,540
Mr Zhang,

487
00:28:38,970 --> 00:28:39,930
Do you also feel that

488
00:28:40,020 --> 00:28:41,350
