490
00:28:50,210 --> 00:28:51,930
Does it matter what I think?

491
00:28:52,020 --> 00:28:54,420
Anyway, everyone
thinks I'm fooling around.

492
00:28:54,510 --> 00:28:55,650
At least in my opinion,

493
00:28:56,030 --> 00:28:57,260
you aren't nothing

494
00:28:57,350 --> 00:28:58,710
or a useless person either.

495
00:28:59,390 --> 00:29:00,470
You just haven't found

496
00:29:00,560 --> 00:29:01,660
your place yet.

497
00:29:04,910 --> 00:29:06,990
Just like the theory of
"casual" you told me about.

498
00:29:07,830 --> 00:29:09,450
