I'll try my best to help you.

507
00:29:21,570 --> 00:29:22,980
Let's start with a degree certificate.

508
00:29:23,590 --> 00:29:26,000
I believe that when the contract ends,

509
00:29:26,200 --> 00:29:26,770
you're sure to find

510
00:29:26,860 --> 00:29:28,320
your own life direction.

511
00:29:32,740 --> 00:29:33,620
